Nonto R Women in Comedy: Nonto R continues to bring us the Women in Comedy series featuring herself and fellow comedians including Nina Hastie, Noko Moswete and Khanyisa Bunu. Details: The show will take place on February 1 at the BAT Centre, 45 Maritime Place, Small Craft Harbour, Victoria Embankment, Durban.
